  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nTruffle Contract still uses Browserify to build.  This is a problem because Browserify is incompatible with certain features of ES2019 and is no longer being updated.  This is why in #4652 I could only update the TS target to ES2018, not ES2019 as I had planned.  I expect that as time goes on this problem will only get worse.  We should remove Browserify and replace it with Webpack or something.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.30",
